casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Dettelbach.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Dettelbach (1988), 39 Ohio St. 3d 606.]

(No. D.R. 88-6 — Submitted October 19, 1988 — Decided November 23, 1988.)

The resignation of Martin K. Dettelbach as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
